{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_02_03",
  "title": "サニーピース 02 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "それで怜ちゃんは\nプロのダンサーを目指すことにしたんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So Rei-chan‚ you decided\nto become a professional dancer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、高校生になった私は\n大会にも積極的に出場するようになったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ when I became a high school student‚\nI started actively participating in competitions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4333333969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 12.9666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "東京のダンススクールに通っていたんですわよね？\nレッスン料はどうしていたんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were attending a dance school in Tokyo‚ right?\nHow did you pay for the lessons?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5333333969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 19.3333333969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "貯金を切り崩してやりくりしていたわ\n親の援助は受けられないし、受ける気もなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I used my savings.\nI couldn't rely on my parents' support‚ and I didn't want to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6666667302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく大会で結果を出して\n父を見返してやろうと必死で頑張ったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I worked hard‚ desperately trying to get results\nin competitions‚ to make my father acknowledge me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3000000636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 33.6000000636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "怜、この間の大会は三位入賞おめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ congratulations on placing third in the last competition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "期待の新人だって噂になってたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're getting a reputation as a promising newcomer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.5666662216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、でも私なんてまだまだです\n一位の人はレベルが違い過ぎて敵う気がしませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ but I'm still nowhere near good enough.\nThe person who got first place was on a whole other level‚ I didn't stand a chance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1999995549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "平島エリカさんでしょ？　彼女は別格だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean Erika Hirashima? She's in a league of her own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "幾つもの大会で優勝しているプロレベルのダンサーよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's a pro-level dancer who's won countless competitions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1999995549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "平島エリカ……\n優勝するには彼女に勝たなければいけないんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Erika Hirashima…\nSo I have to beat her if I want to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0000023524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 74.3333356857
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 74.3333356857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "平島エリカって聞いたことがある名前ですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Erika Hirashima… I feel like I've heard that name before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4333356857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 80.366669019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "今は有名アーティストのバックダンサーをしてるから\nどこかで会ったことがあるかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's a backup dancer for a famous artist now‚\nso you might have seen her somewhere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8333356857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "エリカとは大会で何度も顔を合わせるうちに\n自然と話すようになって、一緒に練習したりもしたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I ran into Erika a lot at competitions‚\nand we naturally started talking and even practicing together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.8000043869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 94.4000043869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんのライバルだったんだね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So she was your rival‚ Rei-chan~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4000043869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃の私は、父に認めさせるために\n大会で結果を出そうと躍起になってたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ I was desperate to get results in competitions\nto prove myself to my father‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8666710536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 104.1666710536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "今にして考えると、その気持ちだけじゃ\nあんなに頑張れなかったと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but looking back‚ I don't think I could have worked so hard\nwith just that motivation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7333377202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 110.1000043869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "支えてくれたコーチや競い合うライバルがいたから\n私は諦めずにやり抜くことが出来たのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was because I had a coach who supported me and\nrivals to compete with that I was able to persevere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4000043869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 117.5333377202
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、その平島エリカには勝てたんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ were you able to beat this Erika Hirashima?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5333377202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 122.0000043869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "ええ……高校二年の終わりに\n私はエリカに勝って初めて大会で優勝したわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… at the end of my second year of high school‚\nI beat Erika and won my first competition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5333377202,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5833.333333399992,
          "startTime": 131.3666710536
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.8166710536
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.8166710536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "優勝おめでとう。審査員も今日の怜のダンスは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Congratulations on winning. The judges were all praising",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8666710536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "圧倒的だったって褒めちぎってたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "your dancing today‚ Rei‚ saying it was overwhelming.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.2666710536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.6000043869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。エリカからも祝福されました\nプロになって一緒に踊れる日を楽しみにしてるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Erika congratulated me too.\nShe said she's looking forward to the day we can dance together as pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5666710536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "こうして結果を出せて、今まで私がやってきたことは\n間違っていなかったと実感出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Getting these results… it makes me feel like everything\nI've done until now wasn't wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1000043869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.7666710536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "大会で優勝出来て……これで夢に近づけたのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won the competition… Does this mean I'm closer to my dream?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.7666710536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.933344841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "夢ってプロのダンサーになること？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your dream is to become a professional dancer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.933344841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、私はダンスが好きなので\n将来はダンスで食べていけるようになりたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I love dancing‚\nso I want to be able to make a living from it in the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.7000054042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
