      "text": "優勝トロフィーよ\n私、ダンスの大会で優勝したの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a trophy for winning.\nI won a dance competition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.2333356857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
