        "en": "Everyone praised my dancing.\nNow you too‚ Dad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.8000023524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.2333428065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-reidad002.m4a",
      "text": "くだらない。お前はいつまで遊んでいるつもりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ridiculous. How long are you going to keep messing around?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.2333428065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-reidad003.m4a",
      "text": "そんな無駄なことをしている暇があるなら\nもっと有意義なことに時間を使いなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have time for such pointless things‚\nyou should spend it on something more meaningful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.199998792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 215.1333478927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
