      "text": "諦めずに頑張っていれば、いつかお父さんが\n認めてくれるって信じてたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believed that if I kept working hard without giving up‚\nmy father would eventually acknowledge me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.7000013351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
