      "text": "父はとっくに私への関心を失ってたの。思い通りに\nならない子供のことなんてどうでも良かったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My father had already lost interest in me. He didn't care\nabout a child who wouldn't do as he said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.7333255131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
