      "text": "本当にやりたいことなら、ちゃんと父を説得して\n認めてもらって、堂々と音楽をやればいいのにって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it was something he really wanted to do‚ why didn't he properly\nconvince Dad and get his approval‚ and pursue music openly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.2000247318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 284.7333580652
    },
    {
