      "text": "でも、やっと分かったの\n最初から人の話を聞く気がない人を説得するなんて無理",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I finally understand.\nThere's no way to convince someone who has no intention of listening",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.4666913985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
