      "text": "父を納得させるには\n無視出来ないくらいの成果が必要なんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to you in the first place. To convince my father‚\nI need to achieve results he can't ignore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 296.5666832605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
