    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei029.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃんがしたのと同じように、好きなことを\n職業にして、それで食べていけると証明する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like my brother did‚ I have to make my passion my profession‚\nand prove that I can make a living from it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 306.2333641687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_03-rei030.m4a",
      "text": "それが出来て、初めて父は私のやることを\n認めてくれるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Only then‚ when I've proven myself‚\nwill my father truly acknowledge what I do.",
        "id": ""
      },
